#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.isfinite.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.isfinite"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:1 of
msgid "Test element-wise for finiteness (not infinity or not Not a Number)."
msgstr "逐元素测试有限性（非无穷大或非非数字）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:3 of
msgid "The result is returned as a boolean tensor."
msgstr "结果以布尔张量形式返回。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:5 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，则其形状必须可广播至输入的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:17 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- For scalar input, the result is a new boolean with value True if"
" the input is finite; otherwise the value is False (input is either "
"positive infinity, negative infinity or Not a Number).  For array input, "
"the result is a boolean array with the same dimensions as the input and "
"the values are True if the corresponding element of the input is finite; "
"otherwise the values are False (element is either positive infinity, "
"negative infinity or Not a Number)."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 对于标量输入，如果输入是有限的，则结果是一个值为 True 的新布尔值"
"；否则值为 False（输入为正无穷大、负无穷大或非数字）。对于数组输入，结果"
"是一个与输入维度相同的布尔数组，如果输入的对应元素是有限的，则值为 True；"
"否则值为 False（元素为正无穷大、负无穷大或非数字）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:17 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- For scalar input, the result is a new boolean with value True if"
" the input is finite; otherwise the value is False (input is either "
"positive infinity, negative infinity or Not a Number)."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:21 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For array input, the result is a boolean array with the same dimensions "
"as the input and the values are True if the corresponding element of the "
"input is finite; otherwise the values are False (element is either "
"positive infinity, negative infinity or Not a Number)."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 对于标量输入，如果输入是有限的，则结果是一个值为 True 的新布尔值"
"；否则值为 False（输入为正无穷大、负无穷大或非数字）。对于数组输入，结果"
"是一个与输入维度相同的布尔数组，如果输入的对应元素是有限的，则值为 True；"
"否则值为 False（元素为正无穷大、负无穷大或非数字）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isinf`, :py:obj:`isneginf`, :py:obj:`isposinf`, :py:obj:`isnan`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:31 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:32 of
msgid ""
"Not a Number, positive infinity and negative infinity are considered to "
"be non-finite."
msgstr "非数字、正无穷大和负无穷大被视为非有限。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isfinite.isfinite:35 of
msgid ""
"MaxFrame uses the IEEE Standard for Binary Floating-Point for Arithmetic "
"(IEEE 754). This means that Not a Number is not equivalent to infinity. "
"Also that positive infinity is not equivalent to negative infinity. But "
"infinity is equivalent to positive infinity.  Errors result if the second"
" argument is also supplied when `x` is a scalar input, or if first and "
"second arguments have different shapes."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame 使用 IEEE 二进制浮点数算术标准（IEEE 754）。这意味着非数字不等于"
"无穷大。正无穷大也不等于负无穷大。但无穷大等同于正无穷大。如果在 `x` 为"
"标量输入时提供了第二个参数，或者第一和第二参数形状不同，则会导致错误。"

